meta {
  name: Delete a push provider
  type: http
  seq: 5
}

delete {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/push-providers/{{pushProviderId}}
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Deletes a push provider by `pushProviderId`. If the push provider is currently being used in the org by a custom authenticator, the delete will not be allowed.

**Responses:**
- `204`: No Content
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `409`: Conflict
- `429`:
}
